From: harrytyp <harrytyp@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 26 May 2026 23:37:29 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] HD Costume + Font managers, SMUSH passthrough, OOB
 protection
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- HdCostumeManager + HdFontManager integration (init, cleanup, build)
- renderHDComposite: SMUSH cutscene 8-bit passthrough (isSmushActive)
- renderHDComposite: Step 2.6 — HD costume overlay compositing
- renderHDComposite: OOB protection (clamped srcOffX/Y, blitW/H)
- renderHDComposite: Removed strict _needRedraw gate (consumed by 8-bit)
- charset.cpp: HdFontChar recording hook (disabled, needs integration)
- hd_costume_manager.cpp: sub=1 only, LRU cache 512 (already committed)
- module.mk: Added hd_costume_manager.o, hd_font_manager.o
---
 engines/scumm/charset.cpp | 14 +++++++
 engines/scumm/gfx.cpp     | 85 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 engines/scumm/module.mk   |  2 +
 engines/scumm/scumm.cpp   |  8 ++++
 engines/scumm/scumm.h     | 12 ++++++
 5 files changed, 121 insertions(+)

